HEADWORD: Lyce
<hw>Ly`c⟦eacute⟧e"</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. Cf. <er>Lyceum</er>.]</ety> <def>A French lyceum,
or secondary school for students intermediate between elementary school
and college, supported by the French government, for preparing students
for the university.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> secondary school, lyceum, Gymnasium, middle
school.</syn>⟦br⟧
